profile: With professional, dedicated plumbing service to all major cities and surrounding areas in Alberta, and with some of the best plumbers in the industry, The Gentlemen Plumbers work hard to exceed your expectations and deliver quality. If you need a plumber, call us today for plumbing or heating issues, leaky sinks and faucets, clogged drains, toilet, bathtub and shower repairs, furnace cleaning and repairs, hot water tanks and tankless hot water heaters, furnace installation and maintenance, trenchless pipe repair, camera sewer inspection, and more! We have local branches in Calgary, Edmonton, Red Deer, Lethbridge, and Medicine Hat, with extended service all over Southern Alberta, including Camrose, Sherwood Park, St. Albert, Airdrie, High River, Crossfield, Carstairs, Olds, Innisfail, Wetaskiwin, Leduc, Lacombe, Okotoks, Nanton, Taber, Cardston, Didsbury, Brooks, Crowsnest Pass, Cochrane, Strathmore, Sundre, Three Hills, Ponoka, Fort Macleod, Pincher Creek, Bowden, Fort Saskatchewan, Chestermere, Sylvan Lake, Spruce Grove, and Stony Plain.
service_area: Calgary, Edmonton, Red Deer, Lethbridge, Medicine Hat. See our complete Alberta Wide service area and telephone directory here: Alberta Plumbing Directory
hours: 24 hours per day, 7 days a week

profile: KCP Energy is a solar and energy efficiency company. We specialize in adding solar to your home and retrofitting your home's space heating and hot water system to maximize efficiency. If your water tank is nearing the end of it's life or your furnace is on it's last legs we would love the opportunity to talk to you about installing a highly  efficient solar solution that will save you money and reduce your family's carbon footprint.
hours: 8:00 am till 5:00 pm Monday to Friday
products: Solar electric / PV grid tied system, Solar Hot Water systems, High efficiency boilers, High efficiency water tanks, High efficiency furnaces and fancoils.
services: Home heating and hot water system assessments, Solar assessments, Energy saving opportunities, Design and installation of solar systems, high efficiency heating systems and hot water solutions. Radiant heating, infloor, radiators.
brands: Viessmann solar, Viessmann boilers, Enphase, Sharp, Stelrad and many more
specialities: Helping homeowners save money while reducing their carbon footprint
licenses: Certified solar installer, gas ticket, plumbing
warranty_terms: One year on workmanship plus manufacturer's warranty.
